<item>
            <title>[LU-5998] sanityn test 16: failed with bus error</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5998</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/9760&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/9760&lt;/a&gt; for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4820&quot; title=&quot;extra memcpy in read path&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4820&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4820&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; introduced a regression failure in sanityn test 16 under ZFS configuration:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;000001[0] 1417691232.418605 write      0x80fe90 thru 0x813c02	(0x3d73 bytes)
000002[0] 1417691232.431424 mapread    0x3900b7 thru 0x39dea3	(0xdded bytes)
/usr/lib64/lustre/tests/sanityn.sh: line 384: 20202 Bus error               (core dumped) fsx -c 50 -p $FSXP -N $FSXNUM -l $((SIZE * 256)) -S 0 $file1 $file2
 sanityn test_16: @@@@@@ FAIL: test_16 failed with 135
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Maloo reports:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/66d88dbc-7bfb-11e4-ba0c-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/66d88dbc-7bfb-11e4-ba0c-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/f2ff9596-7e86-11e4-bf5a-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/f2ff9596-7e86-11e4-bf5a-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/92b3c0fa-7e80-11e4-bf5a-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/92b3c0fa-7e80-11e4-bf5a-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/4210c196-7e37-11e4-aa98-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/4210c196-7e37-11e4-aa98-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanityn 16&lt;/p&gt;</description>
